{
  "stem": "6526.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every once in awhile, a week or two weeks used to bring in to feed because-- to feed the poor, because they made a kitchen for the poor.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A soup kitchen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was working in the kitchen with other people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is how we got them in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when it came to make the ghetto, it was made the ghetto wherever you lived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If a Jew lived, let's say 300 yards among the Poles, there was a ghetto also.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He lives there, it's a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So that helped a lot.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And compared to other towns and places where they had maybe more stronger or less able-- less able men to work with the Germans to convince them that, after all, you are a father, you are a son, how can you stand, how can you do that?",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We did not have that better time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Our house was in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was a lot of houses around near us and around the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was no fence.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was no fence, but each one knew where the ghetto is.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But because people lived outside the ghetto and it was called ghetto, so there was no problem.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then there were time a lot of people from town lived from the village.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They used to go to the farmers in the little village and used to bring in pair of shoes, piece of leather, or a piece of-- a pair of pants, used to sell their own things.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let's say they had bedding.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had bedding for four or five people in the house, and they didn't have a bed to sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
